data.description: Great 3 bedroom, 2 bath home available in south Lakeland. This home sits on a half acre lot and has no HOA! This updated home features a new AC system, new drainfield and a newer roof. Other features include formal living room, dining room and updated kitchen and bathrooms. In the perfectly located kitchen you will find stainless steel appliances and easy access to the family room and formal dining room. Low maintenance tile is throughout the home. This home is in a cul-de-sac and features a huge screened lanai and a large fenced back yard. Make your appointment today to see this great property.
